    "We defined three null prompt templates: (1)",
    "Defining the verbalizer token can be tedious, because domain knowledge and technical expertise about the used PLM is required.",
    "This can be a significant issue, as such a comprehensive knowledge is uncommon in the clinical setting.",
    "Moreover, PET restricts the verbalizer token to a single token.",
    "Hence, an appropriate and intuitive token may not be applicable for a label mapping, if it is not included in the PLM's vocabulary."
